历史天气图显示7月2日东南[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]内存在[[东风波|东风波]]<ref name="documentation">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150930195553/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_dec12.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_dec12.html | title = Documentation of Atlantic Tropical Cyclones Changes in HURDAT | author = Christopher W. Landsea | date = 2012-12 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-26 | location = Miami, Florida | display-authors = etal | archivedate = 2015-09-30 }}</ref>，并于当天发展成热带低气压。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]下午18点左右，气旋增强成热带风暴并向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动，然后达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时100公里、最低[[气压|气压]]995[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]（29.4[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt }}</ref>。整场风暴“自始至终”直径都很小<ref name="1921mwr">{{cite report | work = Weather Bureau | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161221120704/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/mwr_pdf/1921.pdf | archivedate = 2016-12-21 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/mwr_pdf/1921.pdf | title = Summary Of The Hurricanes Of 1919, 1920, and 1921 | author = William P. Day | date = 1921-12 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | pages = 658-659 | accessdate = 2016-12-23 | location = Washington, D.C. }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}7月4日上午11点，气旋以最高强度从[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[圣罗萨县_(佛罗里达州)|圣罗萨县]][[纳瓦拉_(佛罗里达州)|纳瓦拉]]（{{lang|en|Navarre}}）附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。次日清晨，风暴减弱成热带低气压，再于数小时后逐渐消散<ref name="HURDAT" />。{{lang|en|E}}·{{lang|en|E}}·桑德斯渔业公司（{{lang|en|E. E. Saunders Fish Company}}）船队的“鹦鹉螺号”（{{lang|en|Nautilus}}）辅助[[双桅纵帆船|双桅纵帆船]]在佛罗里达州[[彭萨科拉_(佛罗里达州)|彭萨科拉]]被气旋摧毁，造成价值1500美元的损失。“{{lang|en|W}}·{{lang|en|D}}·霍萨克号”（{{lang|en|W.D. Hossack}}）双桅纵帆船的船员弃船逃生，但船之后由“布卢菲尔兹号”（{{lang|en|Bluefields}}）双桅纵帆船和“回声号”（{{lang|en|Echo}}）拖船打捞上岸。此外，风暴还对农作物构成轻微破坏。<ref name="documentation" />
